text: RNE (Spanish: "Radio Nacional de España") (English: "Spain's National Radio") is a Spanish public radio broadcaster. Since 1973 it's integrated on the RTVE group. Now, RNE is made up of 6 radio channels: * Radio Nacional (national radio) - a general radio channel. * Radio clásica (classical radio) - plays classical music * Radio 3 - alternative music and culture * Ràdio 4 - generalist radio channel on Catalan * Radio 5 - information radio channel * Radio exterior (exterior radio): outside Spain's radio service == References == Category:Radio
title: RNE
